/**
 * We keep these listed seperately as we use the lowercase tag names as part
 * of the runtime bundle to detect SVG components
 */
const lowercaseSVGElements = [
    "animate",
    "circle",
    "defs",
    "desc",
    "ellipse",
    "g",
    "image",
    "line",
    "filter",
    "marker",
    "mask",
    "metadata",
    "path",
    "pattern",
    "polygon",
    "polyline",
    "rect",
    "stop",
    "svg",
    "switch",
    "symbol",
    "text",
    "tspan",
    "use",
    "view",
];

export { lowercaseSVGElements };
